file.name: expected_trait_enum_component.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Games
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /totalWar:
    get:
      operationId: getTotalwar
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TotalWar'
  /callOfDuty:
    get:
      operationId: getCallofduty
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CallOfDuty'
components:
  schemas:
    CallOfDuty:
      required:
        - game
        - episode
      type: object
      properties:
        game:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Game'
        episode:
          type: string
          enum:
            - first
            - second
    Game:
      type: string
      enum:
        - action
        - strategy
    TotalWar:
      required:
        - game
        - episode
      type: object
      properties:
        game:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Game'
        episode:
          type: string
          enum:
            - first
            - second
